  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-04 synthetic)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. Model Risk Level 3. Thirteen credibility factors are evaluated; twelve are assessed with full gradation data. One factor — Equivalency of input parameters — is marked not-assessed on the grounds that the team judged it inapplicable to a purely computational COU with no physical test article, yet the encoding incorrectly uses factorStatus 'not-assessed' rather than 'not-applicable', leaving a material epistemic gap at MRL 3.",
